{
  "stem": "5255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She took-- she was a mother all over again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is what happened in September of 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did the rabbi that your father followed survive that bombardment?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally didn't meet him after that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very much hurt because we always were thinking that good people that do good deeds and good things should happen to them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wouldn't consider that as a good thing that happened to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really almost denounced the religiosity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't [NON-ENGLISH] any more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I was observing because of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we had to say Kaddish every day because that-- that was the custom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had to daven and say Kaddish for 11 months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't need a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody-- every Jew can conduct services.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During that time there was a question of, we have to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody has to support us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no-- money ran out, whatever little money we had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the things-- like food and whatever people need for everyday survival, got more expensive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Inflation sets in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the woman that owned the printing and rubber stamp company offered me a partnership.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I knew how to make rubber stamps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people used to come from all over to buy rubber stamps of every description.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I started making money because we started charging prices-- high prices-- because we couldn't replace the raw materials.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They weren't available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is what made me money to survive in the ghetto-- and right after the tragedy that happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
